Pre-Game Insights: Kenya will be taking on Mozambique in the 3rd game of the ICC Men's T20 World Cup Africa Sub Regional Qualifier B, 2024.
The match will be played at the Ruaraka Sports Club Ground, Nairobi on 19th October 2024 at 04:20 PM IST.
Mozambique are playing their first game of this season. In their last 5 games, Mozambique have won 2 games and lost 3.
Kenya are also playing their first game of this season. In their last 5 games, Kenya have won 3 games and lost 2.
The pitch at the Ruaraka Sports Club Ground, Nairobi is a balanced pitch.
Temperature is expected to be around 22.5 °C with 63% humidity. Winds at a speed of 3.06 m/s are expected. There is moderate rain expected which may affect playing conditions.
